            {
                aspect "Integrity Verification"
                details "Implement mechanisms to verify the integrity of mobile code before execution.
                    +b This can include cryptographic checksums or digital signatures."
            {
                aspect "Authenticity Assurance"
                details "Ensure that the mobile code originates from a trusted source and has not been
                    +b altered since its creation or distribution."
            {
                aspect "Execution Restrictions"
                details "Restrict the execution of mobile code to environments where integrity checks
                    +b can be reliably enforced."
